text: hanni pham, this is truely one of the greatest pieces of music ive ever heard in my 15 years of life on this green planet Earth. no, that is a understatement. this is one of the greatest pieces of ART i have laid my two eyes on. this is something otherworldy that i feel as if extra terestial beings have to partake in as without it, they would not truely understand what us homosapiens were capable of. hanni pham, you have to start your own solo career. i am not saying this for my own satisfaction, but i feel as if im speaking for the entire bunny community. we would all like to hear your vocals and that angelic voice you were gifted with on your very own tracks and albums. thank you so much hanni for blessing me with such a soothing cover of an already blessed song. i take lots things for granted and i can notice that is one of my flaws as a human, however, your existence and the fact i was born in the same generation as you to be able to listen to such high quality depicitions of your vocals will be something i will always be grateful for. i listen to you while i excrete feces, take a shower, eat, get ready, and even going to sleep. your songs have their very own spot in my mind. thank you so much for truely changing my perspectivie on life with your music, hanni pham.
